node.text: Following back-to-back hurricanes, the town of Lake Charles in Louisiana was badly damaged and left many homes in need of major repairs. Wayfair and @KellyClarkson teamed up to rebuild the Gomez family home as they continue to recover. Watch the video about their home transformation via our link in bio. #KellyClarksonxWayfair

node.title: Change Starts at Home featuring Kelly Clarkson

node.text: Meet Martha Bergeron. She’s lived in Louisiana all her life, but with back-to-back hurricanes, her home was in need of major repairs. Wayfair and @KellyClarkson teamed up to renovate it into a place she can continue to fill with love and sweet potato pie. Watch the video about her home transformation via our link in bio. #KellyClarksonxWayfair

node.title: Change Starts at Home featuring Kelly Clarkson

node.text: The Bucket List Family has been looking for their dream home...and finally found it, in Hawaii! Follow their journey, in partnership with Home Love Network and Wayfair, to furnish their forever home!
